  <div class="teaser-date">02/15/22</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/what-is-annihilation?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span property="schema:name">What is annihilation?</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>In particle physics, &ldquo;annihilation&rdquo; is a transformation.</p>


</article>

<article role="article" about="/article/are-leptons-all-alike?language_content_entity=und" typeof="schema:Article" class="node node--type-article node--view-mode-teaser">

